'''The Coalition'''，是微软旗下一家位于加拿大温哥华的游戏开发工作室，前身为Zipline Studios、微软游戏工作室温哥华分部（Microsoft Game Studios Vancouver）和黑图斯克工作室（Black Tusk Studios）。<ref>{{cite news |title=Microsoft opens new video game studio in Vancouver |url=http://blogs.vancouversun.com/2012/11/29/microsoft-opens-new-video-game-studio-in-vancouver/ |first=Gillian |last=Shaw |date=Nov 29, 2012 |work=Vancouver Sun |accessdate=Jan 16, 2013 |archive-date=2015-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030090114/http://blogs.vancouversun.com/2012/11/29/microsoft-opens-new-video-game-studio-in-vancouver/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年11月，工作室更名为黑图斯克工作室（Black Tusk Studios），并主要负责创作《光环》的相关作品。<ref>{{cite news |title=Microsoft’s new Black Tusk Studios, headed by ex-EA devs, looking to make the next Halo |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/11/30/microsofts-new-black-tusk-studios-headed-by-ex-ea-devs-looking-to-make-the-next-halo/ |first=T.J. |last=Hafer |date=Nov 30, 2012 |work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |accessdate=Jan 16, 2013 |archive-date=2014-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410004552/http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/11/30/microsofts-new-black-tusk-studios-headed-by-ex-ea-devs-looking-to-make-the-next-halo/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>更名前，该工作室为Microsoft Flight和一个Kinect游戏进行工作。<ref name="polygon2">{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/28/5354334/the-mystery-of-black-tusks-next-big-entertainment-franchise|title=The mystery of Black Tusk's 'next big entertainment franchise'|last=Lien|first=Tracey|date=28 January 2014|work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|accessdate=28 January 2014|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162445/https://www.polygon.com/2014/1/28/5354334/the-mystery-of-black-tusks-next-big-entertainment-franchise|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年1月27日，微软已从[[Epic_Games|Epic Games]]收购游戏系列《战争机器》的版权，黑图斯克工作室将继续开发该系列的游戏。<ref>{{cite press release |author=<!-- Staff writer(s); no by-line. --> |title=Microsoft Studios acquires rights to Gears of War franchise |url=http://news.xbox.com/2014/01/games-microsoft-studios-gears-of-war |publisher=[[Microsoft|Microsoft]] |date=January 27, 2014 |accessdate=January 27, 2014 |archive-date=2015-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015205706/http://news.xbox.com/2014/01/games-microsoft-studios-gears-of-war |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="polygon3">{{cite news|last=McWhertor|first=Michael|title=Microsoft acquires Gears of War from Epic, hires series producer Rod Fergusson|url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/27/5345342/gears-of-war-xbox-one-microsoft-epic-games-rod-fergusson|accessdate=January 27, 2014|newspaper=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|date=Jan 27, 2014|archive-date=2015-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105042337/http://www.polygon.com/2014/1/27/5345342/gears-of-war-xbox-one-microsoft-epic-games-rod-fergusson|dead-url=no}}</ref> 作为《战争机器》收购的一部分，微软聘请了罗德·弗格森（前三部《战争机器》的制作人兼导演）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.totalxbox.com/81168/features/epic-streak-rod-fergusson-on-bringing-gears-of-war-to-xbox-one/|title=Epic streak: Rod Fergusson on bringing Gears of War to Xbox One. Series veteran talks Black Tusk, Bioshock and betraying fans|work=[[Official_Xbox_Magazine|Official Xbox Magazine]]|publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]]|date=13 September 2014|accessdate=24 June 2015|first=Jon|last=Hicks|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140913145434/http://www.totalxbox.com/81168/features/epic-streak-rod-fergusson-on-bringing-gears-of-war-to-xbox-one/|archivedate=2014-09-13|deadurl=yes}}</ref>2015年6月3日，弗格森在Xbox Wire上宣布将黑图斯克工作室更名为The Coalition。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xbox.com/2015/06/games-introducing-the-coalition|title=Introducing The Coalition – A Message from Rod Fergusson|publisher=Xbox Wire|date=3 June 2015|accessdate=3 June 2015|first=Rod|last=Fergusson|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003025109/http://news.xbox.com/2015/06/games-introducing-the-coalition|dead-url=no}}</ref>

